50|$|When nominated, Kagan was Solicitor General of the United States, {{to which}} she had been {{appointed}} by Barack Obama. She had previously been a contender for the retiring <b>David</b> <b>Souter's</b> seat in 2009, but was passed over in favor of current Supreme Court Justice Sonia Sotomayor.|$|R
